{"word":"G4298 - προκόπτω - prokóptō - prok-op'-to - Increase","slug":"G4298","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προκόπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>prokóptō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>prok-op'-to"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Increase"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C0;&#x03C4;&#x03C9; - prokopto&#x0304;</b> - <i>prok-op'-to</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G2875\">G2875</a>; to <i>drive forward</i> (as if by beating), that is, (figuratively and intransitively) to <i>advance</i> (in amount, to <i>grow</i>; in time, to <i>be well along</i>): - increase, proceed, profit, be far spent, wax."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4297\">G4297</a>"}]}